original_title: Ahmad Jamal featuring Yusef Lateef – Live at the Olympia
overview: This set from the legendary jazzmen Ahmad Jamal and Yusef Lateef proves that these veteran musicians have ideas that are as fresh as any they have ever had. Live at the Olympia June 27, 2012 is a set by Jamal at the piano with his quartet, featuring Reginald Veal on double bass, Herlin Riley on drums, and Manolo Badrena on percussion.
title: Ahmad Jamal featuring Yusef Lateef – Live at the Olympia
